  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "chapterTitle": "祖父的园子",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300094500_21_389-691",
          "range": "389-691",
          "rangeStart": 389,
          "rangeEnd": 691,
          "markText": "呼兰河这小城里住着我的祖父。\n我生的时候，祖父已经六十多岁了，我长到四五岁，祖父就快七十了。\n我家有一个大花园，这花园里蜂子、蝴蝶、蜻蜓、蚂蚱，样样都有。蝴蝶有白蝴蝶、黄蝴蝶。这种蝴蝶极小，不太好看。好看的是大红蝴蝶，满身带着金粉。\n蜻蜓是金的，蚂蚱是绿的，蜂子则嗡嗡地飞着，满身绒毛，落到一朵花上，胖圆圆的就和一个小毛球似的不动了。\n花园里边明晃晃的，红的红，绿的绿，新鲜漂亮。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714615924,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-02 10:12:04",
          "chapterUid": 21,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=389&rangeEnd=691",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=389&rangeEnd=691"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_9_2564-2598",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2564-2598",
      "markText": "是凡经过的人都说这狗老死了，或是被咬死了，其实不是，它是被冷落死了。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2564&rangeEnd=2598",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2564&rangeEnd=2598"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_4_1240-1269",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1240-1269",
      "markText": "所以我就向这“温暖”和“爱”的方面，怀着永久的憧憬和追求。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1240&rangeEnd=1269",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1240&rangeEnd=1269"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_4_815-842",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "815-842",
      "markText": "他斜视着你，他那高傲的眼光从鼻梁经过嘴角而后往下流着。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=815&rangeEnd=842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=815&rangeEnd=842"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_3_388-523",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "388-523",
      "markText": "你美丽的栽花的姑娘， 弄得两手污泥不嫌脏吗； 任凭你怎样的栽， 也怕栽不出一只相思的树来。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=388&rangeEnd=523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=388&rangeEnd=523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_4_1131-1180",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1131-1180",
      "markText": "二十岁那年，我就逃出了父亲的家庭。直到现在还是过着流浪的生活。“长大”是“长大”了，而没有“好”。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1131&rangeEnd=1180",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1131&rangeEnd=1180"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_41_1605-1657",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "1605-1657",
      "markText": "鲁迅先生知道自己的健康不成了，工作的时间没有几年了，死了是不要紧的，只要留给人类更多，鲁迅先生就是这样。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1605&rangeEnd=1657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1605&rangeEnd=1657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_19_860-953",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "860-953",
      "markText": "这地方的火烧云变化极多，一会红堂堂的了，一会金洞洞的了，一会半紫半黄的，一会半灰半百合色。葡萄灰、大黄梨、紫茄子，这些颜色天空上边都有。还有些说也说不出来的、见也未曾见过的诸多种的颜色。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=860&rangeEnd=953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=860&rangeEnd=953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_27_783-850",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "783-850",
      "markText": "不料除了后园之外，还有更大的地方，我站在街上，不是看什么热闹，不是看那街上的行人车马，而是心里边想：是不是我将来一个人也可以走得很远？",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=783&rangeEnd=850",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=783&rangeEnd=850"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_21_995-1032",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "995-1032",
      "markText": "祖父戴一个大草帽，我戴一个小草帽，祖父栽花，我就栽花；祖父拔草，我就拔草。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=995&rangeEnd=1032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_15_1714-1787",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "1714-1787",
      "markText": "卖豆芽菜的女子，虽然她疯了还忘不了自己的悲哀，隔三差五地还到庙台上去哭一场，但是一哭完了，仍是得回家去吃饭、睡觉、卖豆芽菜。她仍是平平静静地活着。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1714&rangeEnd=1787",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1714&rangeEnd=1787"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_5_3967-4013",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3967-4013",
      "markText": "祖父猛力打了拉车的，说他欺侮小孩，说他不让小孩坐车让蹲在那里。没有给他钱，从院子把他轰出去。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3967&rangeEnd=4013",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3967&rangeEnd=4013"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_10_1307-1381",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1307-1381",
      "markText": "可弟，我们都是自幼没有见过海的孩子，可是要沿着海往南下去了。海是生疏的，我们怕，但是也就上了海船，漂漂荡荡的，前边没有什么一定的目的，也就往前走了。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1307&rangeEnd=1381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_10_3920-3955",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "3920-3955",
      "markText": "但是从那以后，你的音信一点也没有的。而至今已经四年了，你到底没有信来。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3920&rangeEnd=3955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3920&rangeEnd=3955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_32_2206-2235",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "2206-2235",
      "markText": "祖父装进棺材去的那天早晨，正是后园里玫瑰花开放满树的时候。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2235",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2235"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_7_482-515",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "482-515",
      "markText": "我打算在一年之内，我要翻译关于文学的书籍，在半年之内我能够读报纸。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=482&rangeEnd=515",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=482&rangeEnd=515"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_8_1355-1400",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1355-1400",
      "markText": "有时候，他也不等我说完，他就接下去。我们讲的故事，彼此都好像是讲给自己听，而不是为着对方。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1355&rangeEnd=1400",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1355&rangeEnd=1400"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300094500_13_2585-2675",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "2585-2675",
      "markText": "来往过路的人，一走到这里，就像在人生的路上碰到了打击。是要奋斗的，卷起袖子来，咬紧了牙根，全身的精力集中起来，手抓着人家的板墙，心脏扑通扑通地跳，头不要晕，眼睛不要花，要沉着迎战。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300094500&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2585&rangeEnd=2675",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cee32170813ab8b6ag010977?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2585&rangeEnd=2675"
    },
    {
